stories.title: Zimbabwe v Australia - CricInfo Report
stories.summary:
As expected on current form, Australia beat Zimbabwe in the first of three
one-day internationals, by 83 runs

stories.title: Australia set Zimbabwe 304 for victory
stories.summary: With a weak bowling line-up, Zimbabwe decided their best option was to field on winning the toss
